England second row Dave Attwood will line up against New Zealand at Twickenham on Saturday following the birth of his first child.

Attwood's participation in the QBE Series opener was in doubt due to a delay in his fiancee Bridget going into labour.

However, the Bath forward left England camp on Tuesday afternoon to be at his partner's side and later confirmed on Twitter that the baby had been delivered.

